replies.text: Sir, please understand. My youtube channel is the offiicial continuation of the Sonic Underground Franchise. Tails does not appear within the Sonic Underground universe, so he is not Sonics sidekick. Tail DOES NOT exist in any of my current videos, nor will he ever appear. It just wouldn't make sense and he would feel way out of place with the rest of the characters.  My next animation will be coming within a week but I will tell you now that Tails is not in it. It probably sucks to hear this, but I thought I would tell you so you wouldn't be disapointed.
